data.title: Grace Church Knoxville
data.text: Bryan’s heart races to get people in the game or back in the game to live their lives with a passion knowing “for this is why I was born.” He loves to be part of those moments when people discover and embrace their unique call of God. As Lead Pastor, he is honored and humbled to listen to the Holy Spirit and lead this church in the way that the Lord directs. Bryan received his Master’s of Divinity at Princeton Theological Seminary in Princeton, New Jersey and his Doctorate of Ministry from Reformed Theological Seminary in Orlando, Florida.
